    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Is Hindi Mother of All North Indian Languages? 
    &lt;div id=&#34;is-hindi-mother-of-all-north-indian-languages&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
